spec_data.Name: Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux-Release_Notes-7-en-US
spec_data.Description:
The Release Notes documents the major features and enhancements
implemented in Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.1 and the known issues in
this 7.1 release. For detailed information regarding the changes
between Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6 and 7, consult the Migration
Planning Guide.

Acknowledgements

Red Hat Global Support Services would like to recognize Sterling
Alexander and Michael Everette for their outstanding contributions
in testing Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.
